{"tid":898421,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"［支爆］瑧蓺221呎劏房 北京客1,025萬買入","createTime":"2018-11-11T16:13:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-12T02:01:54.000Z","uid":84771,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a00f484a871a894284d60bfc5223a30a9cafeeb5","tid":898421,"uid":84771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T16:13:54.000Z","msg":"新世界（017）西營盤新盤瑧蓺32樓J室開放式單位，實用面積221方呎，上月中以高達1,025.2萬元成交，呎價46,389元創下全港開放式戶新高價。究竟是誰用千萬買劏房，買家終曝光。<br />\n<br />\n土地註冊處資料顯示，新買家是一名持中國護照的內地客，透過鉅裕貿易有限公司購入該劏房。該內地客姓武，報住北京市海澱區。由於今次以公司名義入市，須支付15%買家印花稅(BSD)及15%雙倍印花稅(DSD)，合共辣稅涉307.6萬元，連樓價總入市成本高達1,332.8萬元，呎價逾6萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181109/58893721?\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181109%2F58893721%3F&d=BpzTxVwg9Yz0Kk8kJrbz2sPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=f813d51c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181109%2F58893721%3F&h=f14809dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181109/58893721?</a>"},{"pid":"81289da045c9267b62c4613d653004dc21af608e","tid":898421,"uid":78791,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T16:15:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"765449fba10f0eee5b8be7c9af32033a710a644c","tid":898421,"uid":84771,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T16:18:42.000Z","msg":"大陸佬資金避險<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n真心唔明"},{"pid":"5a381adbc4c7fdd6db7bce05e7861d68be65272c","tid":898421,"uid":99124,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T16:22:48.000Z","msg":"樓市gogogo好友們快啲襯班弱勢業主未清醒執番個平10%既單位，即買即賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65d3f052c0d5fb8d855cc50152841560e2d7707a","tid":898421,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"765449